'''Uburundi''' n´igihugu kiri muri [[Afrika]] y´ubuseruko. Ikikujwe nu [[Rwanda]] m´uburaruko; [[Tanzania]] m´ubuseruko hamwe na Republika iharanira democratie ya kongo.

==Akahise==
Abashakashatsi bavuga y´uko Uburundi bwamyeho nk´igihugu c´ikukiye kuva mukinjana ca 16. Mu mwaka 1903 niho c´atakaza 
intahe y´ukwikukira igihe hashikiye abadagi. Haheze ingwano y´isi yose ya mbere caciye cegukira igihugu c´ububiligi.
Baciye bagifatanya n´igihugu cu Rwanda: [[Rwanda-urundi]]. Kuwa 1 Mukakaro 1962 niho casubira kuronka intahe yaco 
y´ukwikukira irondewe n´umuganwa [[Louis Rwagasore|Rwagasore Louis]]. Yari umukuru w´umugambwe w'abadasigana [[UPRONA]].

==Ubutunzi==
Uburundi n´igihugu gitunzwe cana cane n´uburimyi hamwe n´ubworozi. Ibice 90% vy´abarundi nico bakora. Kuva 1993 ah´ingwano itereye bifatanijwe n´ibihano yafatiwe 1996 n´ibihugu bibanyi vyo kwugara imbibe; ubukene bwariyongereye cane. N´ico gitumu ubu buri mubihugu 8 vyanyuma bikenye.

